{"tid":786741,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"夢幻原版未拆封Pokemon卡 以這個價格賣出...","createTime":"2018-08-20T07:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T07:00:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53b1da04c6baa880728102522047f0e8afe5f720","tid":786741,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/145850_6ebda72216f780cc36c6f7f14d272e3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F145850_6ebda72216f780cc36c6f7f14d272e3c.png&h=3f6e1e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲王稀有卡片的價格總是令人嘖嘖稱奇，沒想到Pokemon也不遑多讓！近來有一盒1999年原廠出品的未拆封Pokemon卡片，於拍賣會上以5萬6000美元（約新台幣172萬元）成交。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，Huggins＆Scott拍賣會以2萬美元（約新台幣61.4萬元）起標，而原版盒卡內有機會出現罕見且稀有的卡片，今年4月單單是1張「全息噴火龍卡」就賣到5萬5000美元（約新台幣169萬元），所以最後賣到5萬6000美元是很合理的。<br />\n<br />\n外媒還建議Pokemon卡持有者繼續保存卡片，因為收集Pokemon卡有機會可以帶來豐厚的報酬，但前提是收藏的卡片中有較為罕見的，它們比較有可能出現驚人價格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2525048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2525048&d=ijgpc%2BAPKghHsf2yIHXsNP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=64635627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2525048&h=5bc56dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2525048</a>"}]}